summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting deeds to a portion of Block 60, Central Seattle, a portion of Block 20, Lake Side City Addition to the City of Seattle, a portion of Lot 11 Ballard's Four Acre Home Tracts, and a portion of Lot 1 and 2, Motel Addition for street and alley purposes and laying off Aurora Avenue North, 37th Avenue Northwest, 36th Avenue Northeast, and an alley in Block 60, Central Seattle.
